@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kyqagd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.29)))
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.80 / v1 + 0.89) + (v0 + 0.86 - v0 + 0.21)) + 0.95)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.23 * v1 + 0.51)))
    data[tid] = v0
